title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, East Woods]
description: Thickly interwoven branches of oak and maple cast deep night shadows in this portion of the woods. Faint trails seem to cut through the heavy undergrowth of vines and brambles at the foot of the trees, but most appear to dwindle away to nonexistence after a few feet of travel.

Thickly interwoven branches of oak and maple block the sunlight in this portion of the woods.  Faint trails seem to cut through the heavy undergrowth of vines and brambles at the foot of the trees, but most appear to dwindle away to nonexistence after a few feet of travel.
